excluded_licenses: Skype for Business PSTN Domestic Calling
description: Licenses that exclude users from being counted if these are their only licenses
notes: These licenses are typically resource accounts, free services, or communication credits
Users with only these licenses should not be counted in user totals
Users with these licenses plus other paid licenses should still be counted
examples: Microsoft Teams Phone Resource Account - Phone system resource accounts
Microsoft Fabric (Free) - Free tier of Fabric service
Microsoft Power Automate Free - Free tier of Power Automate
Skype for Business PSTN Domestic Calling - Legacy calling service
Microsoft Teams Rooms Pro - Room system licenses
